{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedOutputStreamRef\/writev(vectors:nVectors:bytesWritten:cancellable:)"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedOutputStreamRef","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/BufferedOutputStreamRef\/OutputStreamProtocol-Implementations"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"writev","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"vectors"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GOutputVector"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"text":"nVectors","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int","preciseIdentifier":"s:Si"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"bytesWritten","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"gsize","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gsize","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":">! = nil, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"cancellable"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/CancellableRef","text":"CancellableRef","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV"},{"text":"? = nil) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" -> "},{"text":"Bool","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nVectors"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0 or the sum of all bytes in "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"vectors"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0, returns 0 and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"does nothing.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"On success, the number of bytes written to the stream is returned."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It is not an error if this is not the same as the requested size, as it"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"can happen e.g. on a partial I\/O error, or if there is not enough"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"storage in the stream. All writes block until at least one byte"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"is written or an error occurs; 0 is never returned (unless"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"nVectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is 0 or the sum of all bytes in "},{"code":"vectors","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is 0).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is not "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"text":", then the operation can be cancelled by","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"triggering the cancellable object from another thread. If the operation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"was cancelled, the error "},{"code":"cancelled","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be returned. If an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"operation was partially finished when the operation was cancelled the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"partial result will be returned, without an error.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Some implementations of "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_output_stream_writev()"},{"text":" may have limitations on the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"aggregate buffer size, and will return "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"invalidArgument"},{"type":"text","text":" if these"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"are exceeded. For example, when writing to a local file on UNIX platforms,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the aggregate buffer size must not exceed ","type":"text"},{"code":"G_MAXSSIZE","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" bytes."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"title":"writev(vectors:nVectors:bytesWritten:cancellable:)","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"writev"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"vectors"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UnsafePointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"text":"GOutputVector","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">!, ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"nVectors"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","text":"Int","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"bytesWritten"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"UnsafeMutablePointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:Sp"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@gsize","text":"gsize"},{"kind":"text","text":">!, "},{"text":"cancellable","kind":"externalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14CancellableRefV","text":"CancellableRef"},{"text":"?) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"throws","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Sb","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Bool"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO20OutputStreamProtocolPAAE6writev7vectors8nVectors12bytesWritten11cancellableSbSPySo14_GOutputVectorVGSg_SiSpySuGSgAA14CancellableRefVSgtKF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO23BufferedOutputStreamRefV","symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","extendedModule":"GIO","roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"pa